        <section id="detailed_desc">
            <title>Details</title>
            <dl outputclass="deprecated">
                <dlentry>
                    <dt>Deprecated:</dt>
                    <dd>This method is deprecated. Use the Android native method <xref keyref="TextureView-link" /> instead.</dd>
                </dlentry>
            </dl>
            <p>You can call this method to create a TextureView, which is suitable for scenarios that require scaling, rotation, and parallel coordinate translation of video images, such as screen sharing. The operation and layout of the view are managed by the app, and the Agora SDK renders the view provided by the app.</p>
            <p>To use a TextureView, call this method; to use a SurfaceView, call <xref keyref="CreateRendererView" />.<note type="attention">Call this in the main thread.</note></p>
        </section>
